  "name": "Morrison COU2 — MRL 5 Complete-Profile Clean Package (NC-3)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device at Model Risk Level 5. Full 13-factor assessment: all 13 factors assessed at high rigor (MRL 5), with both requiredLevel and achievedLevel populated, inline AcceptanceCriteria objects, full UQ, and inline SensitivityAnalysis. Decision Accepted with thorough rationale grounded in structured evidence.",
